    C-->>F: "search results 또는 없음"
    F->>G: "공감 초안 생성"
    G-->>F: "response"
    F-->>W: "ChatResponse"
    W-->>A: "최종 응답"
    Note over F: "FastAPI -> WAS write 없음"
